column5: Meant to post this this morning but better late than never...  .....HAPPY BIRTHDAY JACK (NANOOK)...
What he said above goes for me too!
Happy Birthday Jack and all the best !!
Happy Birthday Jack. Hope you have a great day.
All the 'BEST' today Nanook,and many more to ya......
You are doing a fine job of getting old Jack.  Keep up the good work!
Hope ya had a good day Jack, even if you were stripping walls  Maureen

Well, Thank y'all for the best wishes. Spent the day stripping walls in the kitchen and painting the cieling.Then Wifey took me to the 'local' fish/chip restaraunt, always good there. I tell ya................... getting up to 'plenty nine' aint for sissies  [beansies favorite quote Thanks again. See ya'll at Lakair,   Yeah !!
